---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Lion City Locking Library">
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="hero-label">Singapore Campbellocking Archive</p>

    <h1>Lion City Locking Library</h1>

    <p class="hero-description">
      Documenting the past, present, and future of Singapore Campbellocking
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="home-intro">
    <p>
      Lion City Locking Library is an independent digital archive documenting
      the history and evolution of Locking dance in Singapore.
    </p>

    <p>
      Through interviews, timelines, essays, and community memory, this project
      aims to preserve the stories, experiences, and contributions that shaped
      Singapore's Locking scene.
    </p>

    <p>The Funk is now online.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="home-grid">
    <a href="/campbellocking" class="home-card">
      <h2>What is Campbellocking?</h2>
      <p>Learn about the roots of this unique dance style.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/timeline" class="home-card">
      <h2>Timeline</h2>
      <p>
        Explore key eras, events, crews, and milestones in Singapore Locking
        history.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a href="/contributors" class="home-card">
      <h2>Key Contributors</h2>
      <p>
        Recognise the people who shaped and supported Singapore's Locking scene.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a href="/interviews" class="home-card">
      <h2>Lock Talk</h2>
      <p>
        Read oral histories and reflections from dancers, teachers, and
        contributors.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a href="/ask" class="home-card">
      <h2>Ask Anything</h2>
      <p>
        Ask questions and invite the community to share knowledge and memories.
      </p>
    </a>
  </section>
  <section class="featured-quote">
    <blockquote>
      "You have to unlock the lock. You have to unlock the character. You have
      to totally surrender to the music."
    </blockquote>

    <p>~ Chunky</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
